    "attributes": {
        "action": "Ensure fair and transparent faith security funding for all faith communities",
        "additional_details": "Recent announcements show \u00a373.4m funding, with \u00a340m and \u00a328.4m allocated to specific groups, while others share \u00a35m. Greater transparency is needed to ensure all communities feel equally supported, protected, and fairly treated.",
        "background": "Publish clear data on how faith security funding is allocated and ensure all communities can access it fairly. We think this should be done alongside improving transparency, outreach, and support so underrepresented groups, including Hindu community, can apply and receive appropriate protection.",
